claim.claim-text:
1. A device for manufacturing a flexible continuous printing blanket comprising: 
a base; 
an application layer located directly on the base; 
a polymer applicator applying a polymer layer over the flexible application layer so as to form a flexible sleeve, at least one of the application layer and the polymer layer being an innermost layer of the flexible sleeve; and 
a print layer applicator applying a print layer over the flexible sleeve.
